---
title: Harissa Roasted Pumpkin with Spinach Couscous, Herby Mayo & Almonds
description: Couscous is a lovely way to finish the day off, but what if there was a bit of green? Add some spinach to pop against the vibrant orange of
the roasted pumpkin. Finally, crumble little clouds of feta on top for the perfect way to tie this dinner together.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

